    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757697>
    dc:description "Figs. 34-37. Sierracapnia yosemite. Male: Tuolumne River, California: 34. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct, knob on tergum 7 and knobs on tergum 9. 35. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knobs on tergum 9. 36. Epiproct, lateral, apex. 37. Knob on tergum 7, anterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757697/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757679>
    dc:description "Fig. 1-4. Sierracapnia barberi. Male: 1. North Fork Cosumnes River, California. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct. 2. North Fork Cosumnes River, California. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 3. Sierra Canyon Creek, Nevada. Knob on tergum 7, dorsal, anterior. 4. Sierra Canyon Creek, Nevada. Tip of paraprocts and fusion plate (center prong), ventral, terminal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757679/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757685>
    dc:description "Figs. 9-12. Sierracapnia mono. Male: 9. Zephyr Cove, Nevada. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 10. Zephyr Cove, Nevada. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knobs on tergum 9. 11. Slinkard Creek, California. Knob on tergum 7, anterior. 12. Clear Creek, Nevada. Tip of paraprocts and fusion plate showing tube, dorsal, terminal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757685/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4765484>
    dc:description "Figs. 26-33. Sierracapnia washoe sp. n. 26. Jenny Creek, Nevada. Male. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 27. Cedar Hill Canyon Creek, Nevada. Male. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct, knob on tergum 7 and knobs on tergum 9. 28. Cedar Hill Canyon Creek, Nevada. Male. Epiproct, dorsal. 29. Cedar Hill Canyon Creek, Nevada. Male. Epiproct, lateral and knobs on tergum 9. 30. Jenny Creek, Nevada. Male. Knob on tergum 7, anterior. 31. Jenny Creek, Nevada. Male. Epiproct with expanded eversible crest, dorsolateral, terminal. 32. Jenny Creek, Nevada. Male. Tip of paraprocts and fusion plate inserted into epiproct base, terminal. 33. Cedar Hill Canyon Creek, Nevada. Female. Genitalia, subgenital plate on sterna 7 and 8." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4765484/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757693>
    dc:description "Figs. 21-25. Sierracapnia washoe sp. n. Cedar Hill Canyon Creek, Nevada. 21. Male. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct, knob on tergum 7 and knob on tergum 9. 22. Male. Genitalia, lateral, close up, eversible crest, dorsolateral horn, neck and caudal setae. 23. Male. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct, knob on tergum 7 and knobs on tergum 9. 24. Male. Epiproct, dorsal, close up. 25. Female. Genitalia, subgenital plate, sclerotized areas on sterna 7 and 8." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757693/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757689>
    dc:description "Figs. 13-16. Sierracapnia palomar. Male: 13. Headwaters North Fork San Jacinto River, California. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knobs on tergum 9. 14. Headwaters North Fork San Jacinto River, California. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knob on tergum 9. 15. Fry Creek, California. Terminalia, lateral, epiproct, knob on tergum 7 and knob on tergum 9. 16. Fry Creek, California. Knob on tergum 7, dorsolateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757689/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757701>
    dc:description "Fig. 39. Distributional map of Sierracapnia spp.: barberi (red), hornigi (purple), mono (dark green), palomar (light blue), washoe (yellow), and yosemite (dark blue)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4757703>
    dc:description "Fig. 40. Distributional map of Sierracapnia shepardi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4757703/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

